{"tid":1938184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"反送中幫香港起哂全港奶共傀儡，而中國肺炎就幫全球搵哂隱形奶共人仕","createTime":"2020-03-22T11:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T11:37:44.000Z","uid":81236,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b36b8a892be4200cc4301b13a567e2d724fb4199","tid":1938184,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"香港佼佼者有三萬隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球代表就係WHO，各地奶共人仕<br />\n<br />\n全部原形畢露<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份人可能只覺得係民主vs專制<br />\n<br />\n但其實隱含住良幣vs劣幣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊既係藍絲唔單單盲撐政府警察專制者<br />\n<br />\n而係假數字、假數據、假消息、假新聞<br />\n<br />\n隱瞞、造假、甚至篡改病毒發源地逃避責任<br />\n<br />\n居然都有一班藍絲去相信、支持、傳播<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佢地已經成為香港既毒瘤，甚至係中共既支持下向全世界擴散</ins><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過第日生活既世界全部都係假？<br />\n<br />\n只要係對政府警察不利既全部都被變成假？<br />\n<br />\n只係講真話對政府有影響就會被捕被控？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背後唔係單單既民主對極權<br />\n<br />\n而係人類文明良知之爭"},{"pid":"f1a612f98fe113fdeeb887408d9f01e96216fe9d","tid":1938184,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58e14538bdc310cfd90a936518f58e49ad145ed","tid":1938184,"uid":87808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:17:30.000Z","msg":"認住佢地！！"},{"pid":"6e68def7cfd94c0150143909bda3c7ed90400a5a","tid":1938184,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155515d35e4ec3c780bd30467e74231a95b00a2c","tid":1938184,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}